# LegalTab/AdvanceDirectivesTab/NinetyOneDayReviewTab/SafetyPlanTab
# named in the catalogue had ZERO BUG-447 violations (all use
# Button/IconButton consistently). Allowlist entry removed.

# BUG-447-ect-tms (run 4) — closed as verification-only; AST scan
