# 14 candidate onClick sites surfaced by the Plan agent's broad grep
# are on native MUI keyboard-accessible primitives (Button at
# EctTab:846 + TmsTab:273; IconButton at EctTab:883; Chip at
# EctTab:531 + TmsTab:327). The cascade-1 ESLint rule already fires
# on these two files unconditionally (they were never allowlisted),
# so any future Box/Paper/Card/Typography onClick addition would
# fail CI. No allowlist entry needed; this comment IS the
# verification record. Sites manually reviewed 2026-04-28.

